  "text": "Viral copy number in BAL cells was confirmed by real-time quantitative PCR (RT-qPCR). The vMC0 primer sequence was, forward primer: 5′-GCC GAAAGC CAC GTG TGT AA and reverse primer: 5′-AGA TCC CAG CCA GTG GGG TA [CITATION_1] .",
